definition.value: A  hydroxykynurenine  that is kynurenine bearing a hydroxy group at the position 5.
A brassinosteroid that is castasterone in which the oxo group at position 6 has been converted to a hydroxy group (the 6alpha-stereoisomer).
A 3beta-sterol having the structure of campestanol with a hydroxy group at the 6alpha-position.
